No Bake Cheesecake 🧀

Recipe : 
Crushed Marie biscuits mixed with warm butter as the base, topped with a creamy blend of cottage cheese, hung curd, and a hint of natural sweetness from dates/honey. Add juicy mango chunks, a smooth layer of mango purée, and finish with kesar, roasted walnuts, and dried rose petals. Pure bliss in every bite!” 🥭

Recipe : 

Boiled whole wheat spaghetti to start with.
For the pesto: fresh basil leaves, walnuts, garlic, olive oil, salt, and some parmesan if you’ve got it—blend it all up!
In a pan, sauté chopped garlic in olive oil, toss in chili flakes + oregano, then add cherry tomatoes. Now add your pasta, that fresh pesto, a splash of pasta water to get the sauce just right, salt & pepper to taste—mix it well and it’s ready to serve! 🌿🍅🍝✨
